Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは未来を変える力を　夢に見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ノイズの中　聞こえて来た君の泣き声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑っていた　僕の弱さを暴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君の行く道は　君にしか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}違う空　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等は未来へ向かう勇気を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}欲しがって過去に迷う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君が笑うほんとうの現在へ帰り付くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:17.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們夢想著  改變未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:36.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雜音中  傳來你的哭泣聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:47.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揭開我  歡笑之下的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.23,0:00:52.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的前路  只有你能決定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:58.78,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}追逐著  不同的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.85,0:01:07.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我們渴求著前往未來的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:13.33,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}卻為此在過去迷失了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:27.91,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}直至回到你所微笑著的此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色の午後は　ママレイドティーとビスケット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}散らかったトランプで　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}さぁ夢の続きを占いましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いくつのドア　開くのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…サガシモノ　何処ニアル？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気づけば　私は迷子で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}秘密の暗号　君だけに送ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}はやく見つけて　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「私はここだよ。」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:31.14,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}金色的午後  品嘗著柚子茶和餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.29,0:22:37.74,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}收起散落一地的紙牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:46.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}來  占卜夢境的後續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.16,0:22:54.82,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}會打開多少扇大門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.19,0:23:02.77,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}…尋找的東西  究竟在何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只注視著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.95,0:23:11.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只追逐著你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:18.36,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這才發現我迷了路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:26.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只向你送去  秘密的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:29.90,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}快點找到我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.99,0:23:35.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「我在這裡哦。」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.18,0:01:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約完成了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去…改變了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這邊  請快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人渾身是血倒在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:44.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了  請等一下  夏羅大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.36,0:01:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:58.61,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷舊的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  夏羅被綁架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅她怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放心吧  她沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.05,0:02:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為與犯人交涉成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉？什麼交涉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密  你沒必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這種事是常有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅大小姐  您醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼「沒關係的」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一點都不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐她沒事吧  文森特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她沒事  我說過吧  我不會殺她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我們能早點相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就設了個時間限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.13,0:03:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個喜歡收集毒藥的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他給了我一些罕見的毒藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就給她倆試了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連艾可都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不確定這解毒劑是否有效的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會聽我的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:59.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽商先生  我說過我想要那個鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不是想要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把那東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銷毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:14.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的事  大家都不知道就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鈴鐺…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲的記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為阿比斯的力量才能夠具有現實的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  普通的方法是無法破壞它的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銷毀它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你那能否定阿比斯力量  並使其消失的瘋狂帽商
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我面前把它銷毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那鈴鐺銷毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  馬上！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一個理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後繼續活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我要去確認
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能恩准我嗎  雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克…我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒必要聽他擺佈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你…一直以來尋求的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你活下去的理由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你滿足了吧  文森特·奈特雷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你啦  帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把那藥給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好人啊  帽商先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我  最喜歡這樣的你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  文森特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種眼神和你的基爾巴特哥哥一模一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次事件的責任在於我太弱  沒能保護好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…到底發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍帥也要懂得適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別自作多情  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你？  不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論何時都是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為了自己而活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會救你  是因為我怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是出了什麼事  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會被雪莉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你媽媽殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種話  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想幫上扎克斯哥哥忙  才在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克斯…哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？ 奧茲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅把佈雷克叫作「扎克斯哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  以前都是這樣叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然他們並不是真正的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像對哥哥那樣仰慕著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你為什麼會知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫雷姆·魯內特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常來萊因茲華斯家打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和扎克西斯也已經認識十年多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克也有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克這個人怪怪的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前起就是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  完全不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前對人更加冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個無論發生什麼事都不會笑的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你看到了嗎  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快死的時候被夏羅大人發現的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙感覺怪模怪樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把那種怪男人作為客人招待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那種事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管我  別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像受傷的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變了那個男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅大人的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是被雪莉大人那豁達的為人給感化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎克西斯也一點點敞開心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在變得能好好露出笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏羅  你有看到笑臉貓的臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以前被阿比斯的意志奪走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了它  讓我想起許多以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佈雷克在尋求一百年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲也尋求著自己的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.19,0:10:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡叔叔  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家…幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們穿著都很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事  奧斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備把我們拐去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是只有我們才能做到的  重要的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這封信是從拉特維吉學校寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉特維吉學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個國家排名前三的全住宿制學校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  現在在那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我們的艾達在上學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾達？那是什麼東西  能吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還有妹妹啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在這封信的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:54.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜啟  親愛的叔父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈  今天是指哪天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少寫上日期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校的牛腰子派很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個啊  我也很喜歡吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不小心把男生弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  這個小冒失鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PS：我有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈  是嗎  有喜歡的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事  叔叔我絕對不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.79,0:12:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？這是緊急事態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被打扮成這樣是要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向艾達確認信的內容  我們要直接…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入學校！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要潛入嗎？像平常那樣辦個手續見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有那麼多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  那樣太不浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走貝薩流斯家挖的秘道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  這裡沒有人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是拉特維吉學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚狀況  你就給我認命吧  海藻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別煩我  笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.26,0:13:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡大人  學生們走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌  基爾巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變裝很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是學生  奧斯卡大人是教師…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大叔是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變…是變態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說您都不可能扮成學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了  好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是校內有可疑人物哦  埃利奧特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟奧茲他們走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲是會好好享受這種狀況的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能稍微高興點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是為此才帶我們來這裡的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就察覺到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校內是禁止吸煙的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算躲起來吸  也是逃不過雪鈴的鼻子的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:56.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（snowdrop，雪鈴花，有「思念並等待著分別已久之人」的意義）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  風紀委員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩了  叔叔他們跑哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為還蠻好玩的  我是沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不覺得你很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:23.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼不願意和妹妹見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲你…有時也很敏銳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊  把我當白癡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在誇你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是不願意  能見面是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過有點害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…我還沒做好心理準備呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲的事我在之前的信裡已經有說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是那樣  可是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為分別時艾達還很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她已經完全不記得我的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…因為…那時到現在已經過了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在的樣子已經和以前完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是…要是他說「這不是艾達」之類的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲不會說那種話的  絕對不會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在  請坦然面對想要見面的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是對我說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我  這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…那時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:17:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你為什麼不能對自己那樣說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因…為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許頂嘴！你這人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  你可是我的契約者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該為這件事感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你就是你而感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡啊  小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大聲喊出你是我的僕人這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  快喊啊  奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是～艾莉絲的～僕人～」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥…哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾…達…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好久不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和以前一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說  快說  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  艾達還記得我的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為哥哥很高大…很溫柔…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都要帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然記憶是會被美化的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更喜歡現在眼前的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說比記憶中矮了點  
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能好好陪在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觸摸得到  能說話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在…一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都好想見到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.81,0:19:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  雖然有改變的地方  但也有沒變的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  艾達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我分開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姑娘  給我適可而止一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是我的私有物品  是我的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動不動就黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是你僕人啊  笨蛋兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧茲是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便弄成你的私有物品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  海藻頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係已經好到能吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘記來這裡的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？大家談論的可疑人物就是叔叔你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為突然想來看看你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你們沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基爾也是  好久沒像這樣說話了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送的帽子  在用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然在用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？帽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到帽子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艾達送的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜  我知道你想說什麼  不過現在斷定還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果真的是那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾～達～  叔叔我們呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問一下關於信裡寫的PS的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？PS？那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.82,0:20:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙已經做好覺悟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為會讓你輕鬆死掉哦  基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.22,0:20:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  剛才那是…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽人家把話說完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奧茲  別丟下我一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和叔叔他們走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心  好像回到了從前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  艾達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰…是誰在彈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然改編了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這裡面的音樂盒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}小鬼你的罪孽實在太深重了的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}只是不想牽連到別人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.17,0:23:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}糾正主人的言行也是侍從的義務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}說到底這只不過是你的自我滿足罷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我會去死的\N如果只有這個方法的話  我不會猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}小鬼你確確實實是個加害者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}明明完全不瞭解留下的人會有多痛苦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  關於某位侍從之死